      "widgets_values": [
        "A highly realistic interpretation of the input sketch. Preserve the original composition, shapes, and spatial layout, but transform it into a detailed, photorealistic image. Add natural lighting, realistic textures, and physically accurate materials. The scene should look like a real-world photograph based on the sketch. Enhance structure and coherence while respecting the original strokes and forms. Ultra-detailed, high realism, sharp focus, cinematic lighting.\n\nThis is the scene:\na stylized human figure standing upright against a solid light green background. The character has an exaggeratedly large head with pink spiky hair that stands up from the top like a mohawk or punk-style spike-topped hairstyle. Their face is simple: two small circular eyes, a straight nose, and a slightly open mouth showing a thin line for lips—suggesting either surprise or neutrality.\n\nTheir body features are defined by thick black outlines and simplified shading; they wear a short-sleeved jacket with visible stitching lines across the chest and shoulders, suggesting it's not worn over clothing but rather as part of their outfit. This suggests perhaps some kind of costume or armor-like attire due to its bold outline and thicknesses used around joints and torso areas which may be meant to convey strength or power.\n\nOn both arms, there appear to be long appendages extending outward—an elongated form resembling wings or possibly articulated limbs extended away from the body’s centerline. These could represent fantastical creature traits such as flight-capable creatures or even mechanical parts designed into fantasy beings' bodies."
      ],
